Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.15,0:03:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs32}{\fad(0,300)}更
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.15,0:03:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs32}{\fad(0,300)}強大
