Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.15,0:03:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs32}{\fad(0,300)}是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.15,0:03:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs32}{\fad(0,300)}渴望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.15,0:03:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs32}{\fad(0,300)}人類 強大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.15,0:03:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs32}{\fad(0,300)}問誰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.15,0:03:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs32}{\fad(0,300)}想 問
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.15,0:03:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs32}{\fad(0,300)}誰？強
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.15,0:03:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs32}{\fad(0,300)}池袋
